                            <comment id="12410531" author="ggregory@seagullsw.com" created="Wed, 5 Oct 2005 09:01:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;----&lt;del&gt;Original Message&lt;/del&gt;----&lt;br/&gt;
From: Gary Gregory &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:ggregory@seagullsoftware.com&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;ggregory@seagullsoftware.com&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/mail_small.gif&quot; height=&quot;12&quot; width=&quot;13&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
